Lines.Text: Alright, alright. I'll tell you this because I trust you. Take this key. There's a record book in Odral's Helvi chest on the second floor. Stendar have mercy on me if anyone finds out about this.
No %PCRace can intimidate me!
You don't have to say it again. Look, here's key. There's a chest under Fadila's house, near the docks. Just leave me in peace.
Okay, okay. I'll buy my guar hides from House Hlaalu. Just leave me alone.
